text: The 1928 Kentucky Wildcats football team represented the Kentucky Wildcats of the University of Kentucky during the 1928 college football season.https://www.sports- reference.com/cfb/schools/kentucky/1928-schedule.html The team finished the season by tying undefeated Tennessee. ==Schedule== ==References== Kentucky Category:Kentucky Wildcats football seasons Kentucky Wildcats football
